definition.text: Upsampling layer for 2D inputs. Repeats the rows and columns of the data by size[0] and size[1] respectively.

paragraphs.text: Input shape: 4D tensor with shape: - If dataFormat is "channelsLast": [batch, rows, cols, channels] - If dataFormat is "channelsFirst": [batch, channels, rows, cols]

Output shape: 4D tensor with shape: - If dataFormat is "channelsLast": [batch, upsampledRows, upsampledCols, channels] - If dataFormat is "channelsFirst": [batch, channels, upsampledRows, upsampledCols]
